        {"type": "dialogue", "speaker": "Character Name From Cast", "text": "Spoken words only, no quote marks, no said-X tags."},
        {"type": "narration", "text": "More prose."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "{{ chapter_id }}_s2",
      "location_hint": "...",
      "beats": []
    }
  ]
}

Field-name rules:
- Top-level keys MUST be exactly: "chapter_id", "scenes".
- Each scene MUST have keys: "scene_id", "location_hint", "beats". `scene_id` MUST follow the pattern `{{ chapter_id }}_s<N>` where N starts at 1 and increments.
- Each beat MUST have keys: "type" (one of "narration" or "dialogue"), "text". Dialogue beats additionally MUST have a "speaker" key with a name from the cast (or "Unknown" if unattributable).
- Do NOT add extra keys (no "scene_number", no "id", no "act", no "line_number").

